lead_paragraph: Establishment Republicans and a right-wing group of former spies and special forces operatives that says it is nonpartisan but has historical Republican ties are raising a ruckus over Hillary Rodham Clinton's handling of the 2012 assault on U.S. installations in Benghazi, Libya.

headline.main: Hillary Clinton Faces New Barrage From the Right Over Benghazi
headline.print_headline: Hillary Clinton Faces New Barrage From the Right Over Benghazi
